msgid "12100:[name]拓巳[line]「この部屋に……ある……」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]拓巳[line]It's... in this room.[%p]"

msgid "12200:七海のケータイ電話が、この部屋に。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:Nanami's phone was somewhere in my room.[%p]"

msgid "12300:どうして？[linebreak]七海が忘れていったの？[linebreak]それとも――[%p]"
msgstr "12300:Why? Had Nanami found it? Or...[%p]"

msgid "12400:『Ｐ．Ｓ．\u3000ところでプレゼントは受け取ってくれた？』[%p]"
msgstr "12400:P.S. Did you get my present?[%p]"

msgid "12500:ウソだ……ウソに決まってる……[linebreak]いくらなんでもそんなのは……無茶苦茶だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:No... That had to be a lie. There was no way this could be real.[%p]"

msgid "12600:僕は、ケータイを持つ手をのろのろと下ろした。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:I lowered my phone slowly.[%p]"

msgid "12700:まばたきもできず。[linebreak]のどはカラカラに渇いて。[linebreak]それでも、音の出所を探す。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:I couldn't even blink. My throat was parched. But still, I looked for the source of the sound.[%p]"

msgid "12800:今度はゆっくりと、ゆっくりと、この部屋に散乱している物へひとつひとつ順に目を移していく。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:This time I looked around slowly, slowly, my eyes landing on each and every object scattered about the room.[%p]"

msgid "12900:部屋を片付けようとしなかったこれまでの自分を激しく恨んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:I hated myself, violently, for not cleaning before.[%p]"

msgid "13000:もっと整理しておけば、どこから聞こえてくるのかすぐに分かったのに……。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:If the place wasn't such a mess, I'd be able to tell where it was coming from immediately.[%p]"

msgid "13100:音は、いったい、どこから――[%p]"
msgstr "13100:Where was the sound coming from?[%p]"

msgid "13200:この箱……[%p]"
msgstr "13200:This box...[%p]"

msgid "13300:この中から、メロディが聞こえてくる……。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:The sound was coming from inside this box.[%p]"

msgid "13400:エロゲーの箱をふたつ並べたくらいのサイズ。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:It was the size of two h-game boxes side by side.[%p]"

msgid "13500:ネット通販の箱かと思ったけど、なんのプリントもされていない。差出人などが書かれた伝票も貼られていない。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:I thought it was from something I'd bought online, but there was nothing printed on it. There was no address label, either.[%p]"

msgid "13600:だけどしっかりとガムテープで封をしてある。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:But it was sealed tightly with tape.[%p]"

msgid "13700:こんな大きな箱、前からここに置いてあったっけ？[linebreak]地震でベッドの上から崩れ落ちてきた？[%p]"
msgstr "13700:Had this big box always been here? Did it fall off the bed in the earthquake?[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]拓巳[line]「……いや……」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]拓巳[line]No...[%p]"

msgid "13900:そもそも、こんな箱、見たことがない。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:I'd never seen this box before.[%p]"

msgid "14000:通販の箱なら、届いたらすぐに開けるし。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:I always opened anything I ordered online right away, too.[%p]"

msgid "14100:オークションの出品物なら、封をしたらすぐに発送しちゃうし。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:And if it was something I'd sold at an online auction, I'd have shipped it off right after I wrapped it up.[%p]"

msgid "14200:七海からの差し入れっていうのも考えたけど、こんなダンボール箱で七海がなにかを持ってきたなんていう記憶はない。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I thought that maybe Nanami had brought me some food or something, but I didn't remember her bringing me a box this big.[%p]"

msgid "14300:つまりは――[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Which meant...[%p]"

msgid "14400:さっき、僕が学校へ行っていた、ほんの一時間ぐらいの間に……[%p]"
msgstr "14400:that in the hour or so when I'd been at school...[%p]"

msgid "14500:誰かが、ここへ来た――[%p]"
msgstr "14500:someone had been here.[%p]"

msgid "14600:『プレゼントを贈るよ』[%p]"
msgstr "14600:I'm sending you a present.[%p]"

msgid "14700:『喜んでもらえると嬉しい』[%p]"
msgstr "14700:I hope you like it.[%p]"

msgid "14800:胸の動悸が激しくなってくる。[linebreak]慌てて扉の施錠を確認する。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:My heart started pounding faster. I quickly checked the lock on the door.[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]拓巳[line]「はあ……はあ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]拓巳[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "15000:ゾワリと、悪寒が背中を走る。[%p]"
msgstr "15000:A cold chill ran down my back.[%p]"

msgid "15100:さっき、フラフラとこのベースから外に出たとき――[linebreak]僕は、この扉に鍵をかけた覚えがない。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:I didn't remember locking the door when I'd staggered out of the Base earlier today.[%p]"

msgid "15200:それも当然だ。[linebreak]あのときの僕は、刺すような頭痛に苛まれて、[linebreak]意識が朦朧としていたんだから……。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I'd never even thought about it. I'd barely even been conscious, thanks to that terrible, stabbing headache.[%p]"

msgid "15300:学校から戻ってくる一時間の間、この部屋は鍵が開きっぱなしで。[linebreak]誰でも出入りし放題だった。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:The door had been completely unlocked for the hour I'd been gone. Anybody who wanted to could've come in.[%p]"

msgid "15400:……『将軍』が、来たの？[linebreak]ここに？[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Had Shogun been here? Had he come into my home?[%p]"

msgid "15500:改めて箱を見る。[linebreak]メロディはいまだに鳴り続けている。[linebreak]この中に、七海のケータイが入っている。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:I looked at the box again. The melody was still playing. Nanami's phone was inside.[%p]"

msgid "15600:僕は、恐る恐るそのダンボール箱を持ち上げてみた。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:I gingerly picked up the cardboard box.[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]拓巳[line]「っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]拓巳[line]...![%p]"

msgid "15800:重い……。[linebreak]ケータイが入ってるだけとは思えない重さだ。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:It was heavy. It was far too heavy to hold just a phone.[%p]"

msgid "15900:体感でだけど、５００ｍｌのジュースと同じくらい。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:It felt like it weighed about the same as a 500ml bottle of juice.[%p]"

msgid "16000:この箱を開けることを、僕は躊躇した。[linebreak]すごく……イヤな予感がする……[%p]"
msgstr "16000:I hesitated to open it. Something felt very, very wrong.[%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]拓巳[line]「こんなの……」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]拓巳[line]I don't...[%p]"

msgid "16200:[name]拓巳[line]「開きたくないよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "16200:[name]拓巳[line]I don't want to open it.[%p]"

msgid "16300:でも、開けずになんとかする方法が思い浮かばない。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:But I couldn't think of a way to avoid it.[%p]"

msgid "16400:それに、七海のことが心配だ。[linebreak]あんな生意気なヤツだけど……[linebreak]それでも、妹なんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:And I was worried about Nanami, too. She was a little brat, but she was still my sister.[%p]"

msgid "16500:その七海のケータイが、ここに入っている。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:Nanami's phone was inside this box.[%p]"

msgid "16600:それは言い換えれば――[linebreak]七海が何者かにケータイを奪われたっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:Which meant... that someone had stolen it from her.[%p]"

msgid "16700:『では七海ちゃん救出クエストを始めよう』[%p]"
msgstr "16700:It's time to begin the quest to save Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "16800:『将軍』のメールに、そうあった……。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:That's what Shogun's email had said.[%p]"

msgid "16900:時計を見る。[linebreak]今は１９時半過ぎ。指定時間まであと１時間半。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:I looked at the clock. It was half past 7:00 PM. I had just an hour and a half until the designated time.[%p]"

msgid "17000:七海の身が……危ない……かもしれない……。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:Maybe Nanami... was in danger?[%p]"

msgid "17100:開けるしか……ないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:I had to open it.[%p]"

msgid "17200:[name]拓巳[line]「はあっ……はあっ……」[%p]"
msgstr "17200:[name]拓巳[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "17300:動悸がおさまらない。[linebreak]脂汗が額からダラダラと流れ始める。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:The sensation of my heart pounding wouldn't go away. The sweat was pouring off my forehead.[%p]"

msgid "17400:僕はその汗を手の甲で拭うと、うめき声を上げながらも、雑に貼られたガムテープをそろそろと引き剥がした。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:I wiped the sweat away with the back of my hand, and let out a moan as I started to strip off the tape.[%p]"

msgid "17500:[name]拓巳[line]「イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……[linebreak]イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……[linebreak]イヤだ……イヤだ……イヤだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "17500:[name]拓巳[line]No... No... No... No... No... No... No... No... No... No... No...[%p]"

msgid "17600:祈るようにつぶやきながら、フタを開く。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:I whispered in prayer as I opened the lid.[%p]"

msgid "17700:中に入っていたのは、アルミホイルに包まれた塊だった。ご丁寧に緩衝材も一緒に詰め込まれている。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:Inside the box was a lump of aluminum foil. They'd even put packing peanuts around it.[%p]"

msgid "17800:恐る恐る箱の中をのぞき込んでみるけど、ケータイは見当たらない。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:Holding back my terror, I looked inside the box, but there was no sign of the phone.[%p]"

msgid "17900:メロディが聞こえるのは、[linebreak]アルミホイルの塊の中。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:The melody was coming from within the foil.[%p]"

msgid "18000:汗が目に入って、痛みが走る。[linebreak]気が付けば全身汗だくだった。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:Sweat got in my eyes and stung. I realized my whole body was covered in sweat.[%p]"

msgid "18100:うう、もうヤダ……[linebreak]なんで僕ばっかりこんな目に……[%p]"
msgstr "18100:Please... just make this all stop happening. Why was I the only one this ever happened to?[%p]"

msgid "18200:泣き言を言いそうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:I felt like crying and complaining to somebody.[%p]"

msgid "18300:星来たんに救いの言葉を求めるけど、なにも言ってくれない。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:I looked to Seira-tan for words of encouragement, but she was silent.[%p]"

msgid "18400:星来たんとの妄想会話ができないくらいに、僕の頭の中はいろいろな妄想が渦巻いて爆発しそうだった。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:My head was so full of terrible delusions that I couldn't even imagine her speaking to me.[%p]"

msgid "18500:気持ちが昂ぶり、思考回路が焼き切れそうだ……。[linebreak]でもケータイの呑気なメロディが、容赦なく僕を急き立てる。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:I was so tense that my mind was on the verge of shorting out, but the cheerful melody of the phone kept driving me on.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]拓巳[line]「はあはあ……あ、開ける……ぞ……はあ……はあ……」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]拓巳[line]Hahh... Hahh... Hahh... I'm gonna open it. Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "18700:僕は覚悟を決めると、指でアルミホイルの端をつまみ、[%p]"
msgstr "18700:I steeled my nerves and grabbed the edge of the foil with my fingers.[%p]"

msgid "18800:目を閉じ、息を止めて、[%p]"
msgstr "18800:I closed my eyes, held my breath,[%p]"

msgid "18900:一気にアルミホイルを引き裂いた――[%p]"
msgstr "18900:and ripped off the foil.[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "19100:メロディが今までよりはっきり聞こえてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:The melody was louder and clearer than ever.[%p]"

msgid "19200:目を開くのが怖い……。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:I was afraid to open my eyes.[%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]拓巳[line]「ううう……はあはあ……はあっはあっ……うううう……くはっはあっ……はあっ……」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]拓巳[line]Ugh... Hahh... Hahh... Hahh... Ghaahh…[%p]"

msgid "19400:息を整えようとするけど、ちっともうまくいかない……。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:I tried to catch my breath, but it wasn't working.[%p]"

msgid "19500:大丈夫だ、大丈夫、イヤなことなんてなにもない。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:It's fine. It's fine. There's nothing to be worried about.[%p]"

msgid "19600:どうせ七海のイタズラだ。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:This was just some prank of Nanami's, right?[%p]"

msgid "19700:そのうち七海が笑顔で“やーい、引っかかったー”とか言ってこの部屋に入ってくるに違いない。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:Any second now, she was going to walk in and yell, “Gotcha!”[%p]"

msgid "19800:そうだ、きっとそうだ。それしか考えられない。[%p]"
msgstr "19800:Yeah. That was what would happen. It was the only explanation.[%p]"

msgid "19900:もしそうなら思い切り叱ってやる。そして二度と口を利いてやらないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "19900:If she came in, I was going to scream at her. And then I'd never speak to her again.[%p]"

msgid "20000:そうだろ、そうだって言ってよ、七海――[%p]"
msgstr "20000:That's right... Tell me I'm right, Nanami.[%p]"

msgid "20100:[name]拓巳[line]「うううう……」[%p]"
msgstr "20100:[name]拓巳[line]Uuuh.....[%p]"

msgid "20200:これ以上、目を閉じて暗闇を見つめ続けることに耐えきれなかった。[linebreak]見ないことで、逆にイヤな妄想ばかりが脳裏に浮かぶ。[%p]"
msgstr "20200:I couldn't keep my eyes closed anymore. Staring into the darkness was too much for me. The fact that I couldn't see it was just making the awful delusions worse.[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]拓巳[line]「はあっ……はあっ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]拓巳[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]"

msgid "20400:だから、僕は――[%p]"
msgstr "20400:So, I...[%p]"

msgid "20500:そっと――[%p]"
msgstr "20500:slowly...[%p]"

msgid "20600:まぶたを――[%p]"
msgstr "20600:opened...[%p]"

msgid "20700:開けて――[%p]"
msgstr "20700:my eyes...[%p]"

msgid "20800:見た――[%p]"
msgstr "20800:and saw.[%p]"

msgid "20900:そこにあったのは、[%p]"
msgstr "20900:What I saw was...[%p]"

msgid "21000:手首。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:a hand.[%p]"

msgid "21100:キレイに切断された、か細い手。[%p]"
msgstr "21100:A small, cleanly-severed hand.[%p]"

msgid "21200:その手が握っているのは、僕とお揃いのケータイ。[%p]"
msgstr "21200:It was holding the same model phone I had.[%p]"

msgid "21300:その手首にはめられているのは、[%p]"
msgstr "21300:And on the wrist...[%p]"

msgid "21400:[name]七海[line]「へえ〜、かわいいバングルじゃん」[%p]"
msgstr "21400:[name]七海[line]Hey, this is cute![%p]"

msgid "21500:[name]七海[line]「じゃあさ、これナナにちょうだい！」[%p]"
msgstr "21500:[name]七海[line]Okay, give it to me, then![%p]"

msgid "21600:[name]七海[line]「へっへ〜。おにぃ、どう？\u3000似合う？」[%p]"
msgstr "21600:[name]七海[line]Heheh. Well, Brother? Does it look good on me?[%p]"

msgid "21700:黄色い革のバンド部分が紅く染まってしまった、[%p]"
msgstr "21700:A bangle...[%p]"

msgid "21800:バングル――[%p]"
msgstr "21800:Its yellow band was stained red with blood.[%p]"

msgid "21900:[name]拓巳[line]「うわああーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー！！！！！！」[%p]"
msgstr "21900:[name]拓巳[line]Uwaaaaaaaaah![%p]"

msgid "22000:そこにあったのは、[%p]"
msgstr "22000:What I saw was...[%p]"

msgid "22100:僕とお揃いのケータイ。[%p]"
msgstr "22100:the same model of phone that I had.[%p]"

msgid "22200:血が、べっとりと、こびり付いていて――[%p]"
msgstr "22200:It was bloodstained.[%p]"

msgid "22300:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あああぁぁぁ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "22300:[name]拓巳[line]Aaaaaaaah![%p]"

msgid "22400:それがなにを意味するのかなんて、分かりきったことだった。[%p]"
msgstr "22400:I knew exactly what that meant.[%p]"

